snippet.title: Goat Simulator 3 – Pre-udder Trailer
snippet.description: There’s nowhere to hide now - Pilgor has you in her sights. Goat Simulator 3 launches on November 17th. Pre-order your digital copy now on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S or Epic Games Store.
